@startuml
title Component Diagram for Analysis Service (Current-State)

skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Arial"

queue "Kafka\nsmap.collector.output" as kafka_in <<System>>
queue "Kafka\nanalytics.*" as kafka_out <<System>>
database "PostgreSQL\nschema_analysis" as postgres <<System>>
database "Redis Cache" as redis <<System>>

package "Analysis Service" {
  [ConsumerServer] as consumer
  [ConsumerRegistry] as registry
  [Ingestion UseCase] as ingestion_uc
  [Pipeline UseCase] as pipeline_uc
  [NLPBatchEnricher] as nlp_uc
  [Contract Publisher] as contract_pub
  [PostInsight UseCase] as post_insight_uc
}

kafka_in -[#blue]> consumer : consume UAP
consumer --> registry
consumer --> ingestion_uc
consumer --> pipeline_uc
pipeline_uc --> nlp_uc
consumer --> post_insight_uc
consumer --> contract_pub
post_insight_uc -[#green]> postgres : persist insights
contract_pub -[#blue]> kafka_out : publish analytics topics
consumer -[#red]> redis : optional cache / health usage

note right of pipeline_uc
Current execution model:
- parse UAP / ingest flat payload
- resolve domain_type_code overlay
- asyncio.to_thread(pipeline.run)
- persist and publish per NLPFact
end note

@enduml
